description.author: Cabal Development Team <cabal-devel@haskell.org>
description.synopsis: A framework for packaging Haskell software
description.description:
The Haskell Common Architecture for Building Applications and
Libraries: a framework defining a common interface for authors to more
easily build their Haskell applications in a portable way.

The Haskell Cabal is part of a larger infrastructure for distributing,
organizing, and cataloging Haskell libraries and tools.

package-flags.name: parsec-struct-diff
package-flags.description: Use StructDiff in parsec tests. Affects only parsec tests.
